Package: gopher
Title: tidymodels-Compatible Gaussian Process Model Zoo
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Felix", "Sigmar", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "felix.sigmar@example.com"))
Description: A gateway to various Gaussian Process (GP) packages available on
    CRAN, including gstat, fields, GPvecchia, and spNNGP. Provides a unified
    tidymodels-native interface through parsnip for model parameter adjustment
    and hyperparameter tuning. Supports spatial-only and spatiotemporal
    Kriging, sf inputs, prediction capabilities, and covariates for residual
    Gaussian Process (Universal Kriging) models. Parameters are automatically
    matched between the unified Kriging-centered argument names in gstat and
    the formulaic arguments used in other packages for the same construct.
